install packagecontrol , do following for sidebar and theme

setui in packagecontrol == https://packagecontrol.io/packages/Seti_UI  (make change in settings of user , not in package settings)

"preferences.sublime.settings-User" file should look like :
{
	"caret_extra_bottom": 3,
	"caret_extra_top": 3,
	"caret_extra_width": 2,
	"color_scheme": "Packages/Theme - Spaceblack/Color Schemes/Spaceblack-alt.tmTheme",
	"font_size": 11,
	"highlight_line": true,
	"ignored_packages":
	[
		"Vintage"
	],
	"overlay_scroll_bars": "enabled",
	"theme": "Seti.sublime-theme"
}
install theme :
theme == spacegray / spaceblack